	<div class="commentBody">
		<div id="comment_body_64246886">And part of the issue is the objections can be done sequentially. <br> <br>
So you file your first complaint, let the developer work through that issue over the course of a couple months. Then file your second complaint, and that takes a couple of months.<br> <br>
Wash, Rinse, Repeat.<br> <br>
Suddenly very few developers have the stomach to develop in that area. And people wonder why there isn't any development in that area of the country.</div>
	</div>

